<p class="ql-align-center">家国情、传统韵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青春意、进取心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">共迎20周年校庆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201016/eb4d04bb300c4ef3bc3ee64b39cb9401.png" max-width="600" /></p>
