<p class="ql-align-justify">展现着他们的青春活力；</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">用活力四射的表演，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">引来阵阵惊叹欢呼。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">他们迈着矫健的步伐，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">喊着震天的口号，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">演绎着青春之歌，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">将更高、更快、更强的体育精神</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">继承并升华。</p>
